# Syntrace Workspace

Dual-inheritance knowledge architecture. Folders and markdown only.

| Path | Purpose | Changes |
|------|---------|---------|
| `schema/agents/` | Agent role definitions (responsibilities, invariants) | Rarely |
| `schema/patterns/` | Architectural patterns and playbooks | Rarely |
| `schema/policies/` | Standing rules and quality standards | Rarely |
| `schema/tools.md` | Tool definitions and contracts | Rarely |
| `memory/decisions/` | ADR-style records explaining why something changed | When choices are made |
| `memory/episodes/` | Work logs, experiments, retrospectives | After work sessions |
| `memory/insights/` | Distilled reusable knowledge | When patterns emerge |
| `memory/inbox/` | Unsorted captures | Anytime |
| `src/`, `tests/`, `docs/` | Code, tests, technical docs | Normal development |

## Before You Act

1. Check `schema/policies/` for rules relevant to your task.
2. Check `memory/insights/` for prior knowledge on the topic.
3. Check `schema/patterns/` for established workflows.

## After You Finish

Save results using today's date. Follow `_template.md` files in each folder. Every file needs YAML frontmatter with `tags: [...]`.

| What happened | Save to | Filename |
|---------------|---------|----------|
| Design choice made | `memory/decisions/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM-slug.md` |
| Work worth logging | `memory/episodes/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md` |
| Reusable pattern found | `memory/insights/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md` |
| Quick capture | `memory/inbox/` | `YYYY-MM-DD-slug.md` |
| Notable change | `CHANGELOG.md` | Append: `[YYYY-MM-DD] type: description` |

## Invariants

- Never modify `schema/` without a decision record in `memory/decisions/`.
- Filenames: `YYYY-MM-DD` prefix, lowercase, hyphens, no spaces.
- Max ~300 lines per `.md` file.
- Never commit secrets; use `.env`.
- For full reference and frontmatter schemas see `AGENTS.md`.
